{"id":11841,"date":"2016-09-02T08:36:06","date_gmt":"2016-09-02T06:36:06","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/?p=11841"},"modified":"2017-08-20T19:20:54","modified_gmt":"2017-08-20T17:20:54","slug":"spigola-al-limone-ed-erbe","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/2016\/09\/02\/spigola-al-limone-ed-erbe\/","title":{"rendered":"Spigola al limone ed erbe"},"content":{"rendered":"<div itemscope itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Recipe\">\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" itemprop=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11845\" alt=\"spigola-limone-erbe\" title=\"spigola-limone-erbe\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"nomericetta\">\n<h2><span itemprop=\"name\">Spigola alle erbe e limone<\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<div id=\"ingredientitempo\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/1345708687_shopping_cart_ecommerce.png\" alt=\"icona-ingredienti\" title=\"icona-ingredienti\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6520\" \/><br \/>\n<strong>Ingredienti:<\/strong><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">2 filetti di spigola<\/span><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">succo di 1 limone<\/span><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">aglio<\/span><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">foglie miste di menta, rosmarino, prezzemolo, timo e basilico<\/span><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">sale<\/span><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"ingredients\">olio<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/1345709212_clock_alarm.png\" alt=\"icona-tempo\" title=\"icona-tempo\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6521\" \/><br \/>\n<strong>Tempo di preparazione:<\/strong><br \/>\n<meta itemprop=\"prepTime\" content=\"PT5M\">5 minuti preparazione,<br \/>\n<meta itemprop=\"cookTime\" content=\"PT10M\">10 minuti cottura.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/1345708681_food_dinner_plate.png\" alt=\"icona-piatto\" title=\"icona-piatto\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6522\" \/><br \/>\n<strong>Dosi per: <\/strong><br \/>\n<span itemprop=\"recipeYield\">2 persone.<\/span>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"clear: both\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"procedimento\">\n<span itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\"><strong>Procedimento:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Mettere i filetti di spigola in un piatto fondo e coprirli con il succo di limone. Far riposare in frigorifero, coperti con la pellicola, per circa 1 ora.<br \/>\nIn una padella capiente, scaldare l&#8217;olio insieme allo spicco di aglio. Quando \u00e8 caldo, aggiungere la spigola rigirata con la parte interna verso il basso e cuocere per qualche minuto.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-cottura-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"spigola-limone-erbe-cottura\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-11843\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-cottura-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-cottura.jpg 667w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Rigirare dall&#8217;altro lato e aggiungere le erbe tritate insieme e il sale.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-preparazione-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"spigola-limone-erbe-preparazione\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-11844\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-preparazione-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe-preparazione.jpg 667w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Cuocere per qualche minuto e servire.<\/p>\n<p><\/span>\n<\/div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11337\" alt=\"spigola-limone-erbe-aglio\" title=\"spigola-limone-erbe-aglio\" src=\"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/spigola-limone-erbe58.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" \/>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Spigola alle erbe e limone<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[219],"tags":[798],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11841"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11841"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11841\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12200,"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11841\/revisions\/12200"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.it\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11841"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.unacucinatuttaperse.